name: Lose Yourself
description:
Talking too fast
When I (see) my face back there you are
Wondering why
Might not be so
And I can't see your eyes

Days passed me by
Blood is on my head
I don't know why
We could look up
Face the stupid heads
We stare at them
All I want to see
Please lose yourself in me

And I love you
When it's slipping into fantasy
Wondering why
Might not be so
And I can't see your eyes
